c: 41
v: 44
t: "Si Men wa…óuno nde janngeteende e haala ajami, …ďe wi'ayno: \"Ko ha…óno Aayeeje mayre …óen fensitee? E nde wonay e haala ajami, [Nulaa…óo] on wona aarabuujo?\" Maaku: \"Kayre wonannde gom…óim…ďe …ďen, ko nde peewal e cellal\". ∆Āe gom…óinaa …ďen kan, noto hino e noppi ma…ď…ďe …óin, kayre ko nde ni…ďe e dow ma…ď…ďe; …ďen hino noddiree e nokku wo…ó…óu…óo"